room_title: Escape room "Amber Sky 2088 VR" by Sandbox VR in San Francisco
room_description: Amber Sky 2088 is our 3rd and most ambitious experience. Journey from the futuristic city of New Hong Kong and soar through the clouds via Earth's last standing space elevator. Take in the cityscape, the curvature of the Earth, and space itself while escorting a mysterious package that could be humanity's last line of defense from the Rawcor invasion of Earth.
